<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiun Monei pa aw gi chu,
 Mei laka hung gi ding ei tai'
 Tatsa te'n kipahna lasan,
 &quot;Hossana&quot; tin lamtuoh hitiu.

[V2]
 &quot;Hung pai zieng ding ka hi&quot;
 Ti'n Lalpan namtin A hilh ie;
 Kisazo un, nam leh chitin te haw,
 A hung na ding ni a nai tai.

[V3]
 2. Kumsawt lenkawl ni hung suokin,
 Tatsa te'n lei hi achim tau;
 Na gam lopi Zingsawl Aksi,
 Tawh hung vakin aw Lal Isu.

[V4]
 3. Kumsawt lenkawl ni hungsuok in,
 Tatte a liengvai sawt taluou;
 Luonthi hulna thangvan gam nuom,
 Hung kihawng in Salem vang khuo.

[V5]
 4. Thim leh vakin ei tuomsung in,
 Nunnawpna pehbang kim theilo;
 Nawpna Lalpa hung leng inla,
 Na gam nawpna ei neihsak in.</lyrics>
<title>Moneipa Aw!</title>
</song>